        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/heal-alac-willbender/">&lt;p&gt;This is a very accessible build that requires minimal effort to play, where majority of its effects are based on auto-attacks. The end of the auto-attack chain &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9161&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Symbol of Protection rely on &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;558&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Writ of Persistence to provide heals. You may find that DPS is fairly decent (for a healer).&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This build is low cognition, low physical complexity, has very few repetitions and is functional in instanced content. This build requires only one weapon with no requirement of a weapon swap: Hammer!&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;gearing&quot;&gt;Gearing&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;hr&#x2F;&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
